OL,3,CDid women die at the hands of the
OL,4,Cjailed breast surgeon Ian Paterson?
OL,6,FThe inquest hearings, which will
OL,7,Fresume on October 7, are the first
OL,8,Ftime that the deaths of former
OL,9,Fpatients have been examined in
OL,10,Fconnection with Paterson's surgical
OL,11,Fpractices.
OL,13,FHis practices have been the subject of
OL,14,Fmultiple reviews, an inquiry and a
OL,15,Fcriminal trial.
OL,17,FPaterson was jailed in 2017 for
OL,18,Fwounding with intent and unlawfully
OL,19,Fwounding nine women and one man he
OL,20,Ftreated between 1997 and 2011.
