OL,3,CDid women die at the hands of the
OL,4,Cjailed breast surgeon Ian Paterson?
OL,6,FHe convinced cancer patients to
OL,7,Fundergo operations by inventing or
OL,8,Fexaggerating the risks of tumours to
OL,9,Fearn extra money and maintain a
OL,10,Fsuccessful reputation.
OL,12,FSome women had mastectomies who did
OL,13,Fnot even have breast cancer.
OL,15,FAn inquiry was published in 2020.
