OL,3,CDid women die at the hands of the
OL,4,Cjailed breast surgeon Ian Paterson?
OL,6,FIt concluded that Paterson, who was
OL,7,Femployed by the Heart of England NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust and practiced in the
OL,9,Findependent sector at Spire Parkway
OL,10,Fand Spire Little Aston, was also
OL,11,Fcarrying out an unapproved version of
OL,12,Fa mastectomy at hospitals where he
OL,13,Fworked that left patients at risk of
OL,14,Ftheir cancer returning.
OL,16,FThey have become known as "cleavage
OL,17,Fsparing" mastectomies.
