OL,13,Finquiry to the coroner, judge Richard
OL,14,FFoster, investigating whether there is
OL,15,Fany evidence to suspect that any of
OL,16,Fthe former patients of Mr. Paterson
OL,17,Fdied an unnatural death as a result of
OL,18,Fhis actions.
