OL,6,FA total of 62 inquests have been
OL,7,Fopened and adjourned with the coroner
OL,8,Fconfirming that a further 20 cases are
OL,9,Fstill being investigated by a multi-
OL,10,Fdisciplinary team.
OL,12,FThe full hearings are due to start in
OL,13,FOctober this year, with the final
OL,14,Frecommendations due in 2026.
OL,16,FStuart Coyne was contacted by the
OL,17,Fcoroner's office in 2023, 16 years
OL,18,Fafter his wife Cathy died in 2008.
OL,20,FIn a letter, he was told that Cathy's
OL,21,Fdeath was going to be investigated.
