OL,6,FShe says the Government has failed to
OL,7,Fimplement all of the recommendations
OL,8,Fmade in the report and, crucially,
OL,9,Fclaims that the group set up to do so
OL,10,Fhas not met for more than a year.
OL,12,FDebbie said: "People can get away with
OL,13,Fit because they're allowed to get away
OL,14,Fwith it. The governance isn't there,
OL,15,Fthe controls aren't there. The 15
OL,16,Frecommendations have not been fully
OL,17,Fimplemented. They haven't met since
OL,18,FJanuary 2023 so that's how seriously
OL,19,Fthey're taking it. They're not looking
OL,20,Fat it."
